        12
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://floridastateauthority.com/counties/lake-county/paisley-florida/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The nearest official weather station sits 1.5 miles east‑southeast of Paisley’s center, labeled PAISLEY 1.1 ESE.",
